title: Base Raid v1.0.1
description: Base Raid is a 2D base build and defence strategy game. The game will be improved with what the community is looking for.In the game your goal is to build the best base to crush the enemy before it crushes you. Everyone loves having the chance to build what they want to, but people also enjoy destroying other peoples creations. In Base Raid you can build anything you want to with the only limit being the available materials and resources. When youe done building you can then get to the real fun
